{
  "stem": "13911.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, this is the Ukrainian woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Beautiful, beautiful woods.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never saw something like this on this continent, since I came here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And pine needles-- the needles were stuck in that broken shoe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My feet were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were walking-- like, at-- at that time, I met my future husband there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was I and that girl that I survived all this with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my future husband and his brother, they were in the partisans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my husband-- he was a very caring man, like, you before himself, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had to attend to everybody, himself last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He found, somewhere a rag.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wrapped it in my feet, because they were bleeding for the needles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Continuous pine needles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Beautiful.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In-- in normal times, it would be a beautiful sight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you were escaping with your future husband?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- and more people, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were like-- we kept together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If we found a potato, we would cook it in the-- in the woods, when we were still-- in an open fire, and cut it in four, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, we shared everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you met him while you were running east.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but he was from my hometown, mind you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- like I knew-- like I said, the boys were-- Jewish boys in a separate school, Jewish girls in a-- so it's just that I lived on that street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I passed by, and the boys would whistle, look out the window.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew one another, but we were very shy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] even, I-- I used to-- maybe I shouldn't tell it-- I was very romantic, so every-- every, maybe, two weeks, I was in love with somebody else, but God forbid he should know about it.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
